Class Team

java.lang.Object
Team
public class Team extends Object
Name: Abdullah Hakimi Date: January 24th, 2024 Description: This file defines the Team class, which represents a sports team with a roster of players. It includes attributes for the team's name, roster, and maximum number of players, and provides methods to add players, check if a player is in the roster, and iterate over the roster. This class is essential for managing a team's player roster and ensuring compliance with team size limits.
